text: Fyter Fest (2022) was a two-week professional wrestling show made by All Elite Wrestling (AEW). It was held on July 13 and July 20, 2022. The first week took place at the Enmarket Arena in Savannah, Georgia and the second week took place at the Gas South Arena in Duluth, Georgia. Both nights aired as special episodes of Dynamite and Rampage.
